633
00:36:37,200 --> 00:36:40,330
I'm not a monster.

634
00:36:40,330 --> 00:36:43,260
Dave! Dave!

635
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:53,430
You don't need that.

636
00:36:53,430 --> 00:36:57,200
You're a big boy now.

637
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:21,300
Aah!

638
00:37:21,300 --> 00:37:23,760
Aah!

639
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:28,700
Mike!

640
00:37:30,100 --> 00:37:32,600
Mike! Mike!

641
00:37:32,600 --> 00:37:34,200
Stop!

642
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:38,500
No! 

643
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:45,960
M.J.!

644
00:37:55,630 --> 00:37:57,330
M.J.!

645
00:37:57,330 --> 00:38:00,800
Mama!

646
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:03,060
