647
00:38:03,060 --> 00:38:05,560
Dave told me to get out of the car.

648
00:38:05,560 --> 00:38:08,560
Oh!

649
00:38:08,560 --> 00:38:10,000
Mike.

650
00:38:13,630 --> 00:38:16,260
Mike!

651
00:38:19,430 --> 00:38:21,800
Daddy!

