00:39:17,660 --> 00:39:19,530
I can make s'mores.

663
00:39:19,530 --> 00:39:22,030
Would you like that, my little princess?

664
00:39:22,030 --> 00:39:23,560
Yeah!

665
00:39:23,560 --> 00:39:25,630
Yeah.

